## Verified flows
1. **Default role** = `sales`. Dashboard renders 2 inbox sections (10 draft
   quotes + 3 submitted proposals), Business Processes + Quick Actions
   visible.
2. **Switch to `mph`** → Inbox swaps to MPH-only section ("No quotes awaiting
   acceptance" empty state, expected — no SENT_TO_CLIENT fixtures). Business
   Processes + Quick Actions hidden (sales-only `visibleRoles`). Menu filters
   to Home + Quotation + Issuance (Policy Admin + Accounting hidden per
   `allowedRoles`).
3. **Switch to `ops`** → Inbox shows 3 members in `REPAIR_PENDING` with
   correct state-badge rendering. Menu filters to Home + Policy Admin only.

